snippet.title: 'Missing' schoolgirl hid in boyfriend's closet for 5 years | 60 Minutes Australia
snippet.description:
(2003) Natasha Ryan is the girl who came back from the dead.  The girl who ran away from her Queensland home at 14, then simply disappeared.  For years police searched for her, family grieved for her, and then all gave her up for dead when a man confessed to murdering her.   The murder trial was underway, when incredibly - after nearly five years in hiding - Natasha reappeared very much alive and well.  In this exclusive report Natasha Ryan tells her remarkable story to Tara Brown.
